<paragraph id="1843467BFFFCE4264783FAAAFD8DFACC" blockId="9.[178,1086,1310,1378]" pageId="9" pageNumber="1382">
T y p u s m a t e r i a l: 
<typeStatus id="C747F8D9FFFCE4264691FAAAFDE6FA9C" box="[416,517,1310,1330]" pageId="9" pageNumber="1382">Holotypus</typeStatus>
() und 1 - 
<typeStatus id="C747F8D9FFFCE426454CFAAAFD34FA9C" box="[637,727,1310,1330]" pageId="9" pageNumber="1382">Paratypus</typeStatus>
: 
<collectingCountry id="60EB06EBFFFCE42645D1FAAAFCB6FA9C" box="[736,853,1310,1330]" name="Thailand" pageId="9" pageNumber="1382">THAILAND</collectingCountry>
